ygData.messageBody:
Well, I finally made 12th last night. I have yet to
train my Meditation since I continued fighting till I
was comefortable enough that if I died I wouldn't lose
my level.
I have been thinking on my last name for a while and
have narrowed the scope a bit. Cronik likes to travel.
I hate staying in the same zone for too long. With that
in mind can anyone here help me choose a last name?
Something dark, not light like Silverfoot, or
Windrider. Maybe Bloodtoes, or Footsore or Darkstrider.
I like Darkstrider. Any other suggestions welcome.

--
Cronik <Brethren of ill Omen>
Left Hand of Thule the Pain Bringer
12th Season Troll SK
Bertoxxulous

"Greenbloods jus be Froglok trick. Smash'm and dey
blood same color a Froglok. Me smash'm Greenblood
for Thule. Thule make Cronik big feared. Make
smash'm fun."
